  "@type": "ActorManifest",
  "id": "did:web:kanae.etzhayyim.com",
  "name": "kanae",
  "displayName": "鼎 — Global Government Fiscal-Flow Visualization",
  "displayNameJa": "鼎",
  "displayNameEn": "Kanae",
  "description": "kotoba-native global government fiscal-flow visualization substrate. Assembles worldwide fund flows — domestic full chain (appropriation → outlay → subaward → procurement-award → recipient) + inter-governmental (IMF / World Bank / OECD / UN transfers, aid, loans) — into kotoba EAVT as fundFlowEdge datoms, narrates flow subgraphs with Murakumo-only LLM (NON-adjudicating, source-cited), and renders aggregate-first kami-engine WASM visualizations (Sankey / treemap / transfer-globe). Reads the already-IPFS-pinned open-government corpus (ADR-2605263900) + the danjo cross-reference graph (ADR-2605301600 + extension ADR-2605302245); never re-fetches (G3 passive-only). danjo finds, kanae renders. NON-adjudicating (G4 UPL-equivalent). Murakumo-only inference (G7). Aggregate-first (G10). kotoba-native — NO RisingWave / Postgres / Lance as store or read backend (G2/N13; the maps RisingWave backend is NOT a template). Transparent Religious Force discipline (G11, ADR-2605192100 §1.12). kami-engine WASM render-only (G14); no third-party BI, no ad/analytics SDK (G15). 5 cells / 4 Lexicons / 15 gates / 14 non-goals.",
  "descriptionJa": "kotoba-native のグローバル政府資金フロー可視化 substrate。全世界の資金の流れ — 国内フルチェーン (歳出予算→支出→補助→調達落札→受領者) + 国際間 (IMF / 世界銀行 / OECD / UN の移転・援助・融資) — を kotoba EAVT に fundFlowEdge datom として組み立て、フロー部分グラフを Murakumo-only LLM で叙述 (非裁定・出典付き) し、集計優先の kami-engine WASM 可視化 (Sankey / ツリーマップ / 移転グローブ) を描画。既に IPFS pin 済みの open-government corpus (ADR-2605263900) + danjo 相互参照グラフ (ADR-2605301600 + 拡張 ADR-2605302245) を読むのみ。再取得なし (G3 受動取得)。弾正が見つけ、鼎が描く。非裁定 (G4, UPL 等価; 「不正・違反があった」とは断定しない)。Murakumo-only 推論 (G7)。集計優先 (G10)。kotoba-native — RisingWave / Postgres / Lance を store・read backend に禁止 (G2/N13; maps の RisingWave backend は雛形にしない)。Transparent Religious Force 規律 (G11, ADR-2605192100 §1.12)。kami-engine WASM 描画のみ (G14); 第三者 BI 禁止・広告/解析 SDK 禁止 (G15)。名 = 鼎(かなえ); 鼎の軽重を問う — 統べる者の資金記録を公開で量る。三本脚 = 国内予算 / 国内調達 / 国際移転 の三基盤。5 cells / 4 Lexicons / 15 gates / 14 non-goals。",
  "adr": {
