      "N8": "NOT a partisan / electioneering tool",
      "N9": "NOT a per-individual reputation / social-credit score",
      "N10": "NOT a replacement for the state's own audit organs (会計検査院 / GAO / ECA)",
      "N11": "NOT a defamation vector (structurally prevented by G4/G5/G10)",
      "N12": "NOT a vendor-LLM inference path (Murakumo-only)",
      "N13": "NOT a substrate-engine / projection-layer replacement (kotoba canonical; no RisingWave like maps)",
      "N14": "NOT a third-party-BI / Palantir-class fusion dashboard (render = kami-engine WASM)"
    }
  },
